articles.title: Google wins court challenge to the EU's $1.7 billion antitrust fine over ad product - CNBC
articles.description: The European Union's second-highest court on Wednesday said a 1.5 billion euro ($1.7 billion) antitrust fine imposed on Google by regulators should be annulled.
